+  private void handleAd()
+  {
+    if (this.nextRation == null)
+    {
+      if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+        Log.e("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "nextRation is null!");
+      }
+      rotateThreadedDelayed();
+      return;
+    }
+    if (!isConnectInternet())
+    {
+      this.scheduler.schedule(new RotatePriAdRunnable(this), 5L, TimeUnit.SECONDS);
+      return;
+    }
+    String str = String.format("Showing ad:\nname: %s", new Object[] { this.nextRation.name });
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", str);
+    }
+    try
+    {
+      AdViewAdapter.handle(this, this.nextRation);
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (Throwable localThrowable)
+    {
+      if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {

+  public static String getDeviceID(Context paramContext)
+  {

+    public void run()

+          break label230;
+        }
+        String str = KyAdView.this.getString.replaceAll("\\n", "");

+    }

+  public class ClientReport
+    implements Runnable
+  {
+    private String content;
+    private String url;
+    
+    ClientReport(String paramString1, String paramString2)
+    {
+      this.url = paramString1;
+      this.content = paramString2;
+    }
+    
+    public void run()
+    {
+      Object localObject1 = new HttpPost(this.url);
+      ArrayList localArrayList = new ArrayList();
+      localArrayList.add(new BasicNameValuePair("name", this.content));
+      DefaultHttpClient localDefaultHttpClient = new DefaultHttpClient();
+      try
+      {
+        ((HttpPost)localObject1).setEntity(new UrlEncodedFormEntity(localArrayList, "UTF-8"));
+        localObject1 = localDefaultHttpClient.execute((HttpUriRequest)localObject1);
+        if (((HttpResponse)localObject1).getStatusLine().getStatusCode() == 200) {
+          EntityUtils.toString(((HttpResponse)localObject1).getEntity(), "UTF_8");
+        }
+        return;
+      }
+      catch (ClientProtocolException localClientProtocolException)
+      {
+        localClientProtocolException.printStackTrace();
+        return;
+      }
+      catch (UnsupportedEncodingException localUnsupportedEncodingException)
+      {
+        localUnsupportedEncodingException.printStackTrace();
+        return;
+      }
+      catch (IOException localIOException)
+      {
+        localIOException.printStackTrace();
+        return;
+      }
+      finally
+      {
+        localDefaultHttpClient.getConnectionManager().shutdown();
+      }
+    }
+  }

+  public class GifRefresh
+    extends Thread
+  {
+    public GifRefresh() {}
+    
+    public void run()
+    {
+      super.run();
+      for (;;)
+      {
+        if (currentThread().isInterrupted()) {
+          return;
+        }
+        try
+        {
+          sleep(1000L);
+          KyAdView.this.notifyRefreshGif();
+        }
+        catch (InterruptedException localInterruptedException)
+        {
+          for (;;)
+          {
+            currentThread().interrupt();
+          }
+        }
+      }
+    }
+  }

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;

+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;

+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class AdBaiduAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdViewListener
+{
+  private AdService adService = null;
+  private AdView adView = null;
+  
+  public AdBaiduAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST)
+    {
+      AdView.setAppSid("debug");
+      AdView.setAppSec("debug");
+      return;
+    }
+    AdView.setAppSid(paramRation.key);
+    AdView.setAppSec(paramRation.key2);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Baidu");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Activity localActivity;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localActivity = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localActivity == null);
+    localAdViewLayout.removeAllViews();
+    localAdViewLayout.activeRation = localAdViewLayout.nextRation;
+    if (this.ration.key3.compareTo("1") == 0)
+    {
+      this.adService = new AdService(localActivity, AdType.IMAGE, localAdViewLayout, new ViewGroup.LayoutParams(-1, -2), this);
+      return;
+    }
+    this.adService = new AdService(localActivity, AdType.TEXT, localAdViewLayout, new ViewGroup.LayoutParams(-1, -2), this);
+  }
+  
+  public void onAdClick()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.w("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onAdClick");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.reportClick();
+  }
+  
+  public void onAdFailed(String paramString)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.w("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdViewListener.onAdFailed, reason=" + paramString);
+    }
+    paramString = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramString == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramString.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramString.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onAdReady()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.w("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onAdReady");
+    }
+    try
+    {
+      this.adView = this.adService.requestAdView();
+      Object localObject = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+      if (localObject == null) {
+        return;
+      }
+      localObject = ((AdViewLayout)localObject).extra;
+      int i = Color.rgb(((Extra)localObject).bgRed, ((Extra)localObject).bgGreen, ((Extra)localObject).bgBlue);
+      int j = Color.rgb(((Extra)localObject).fgRed, ((Extra)localObject).fgGreen, ((Extra)localObject).fgBlue);
+      this.adView.setBackgroundColor(i);
+      this.adView.setTextColor(j);
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (Exception localException)
+    {
+      Log.w("AdView SDK v1.7.4", localException.getMessage());
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void onAdShow()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.w("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onAdShow");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.reportBaiduImpression();
+  }
+  
+  public void onAdSwitch()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.w("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onAdSwitch");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import com.google.ads.Ad;
+import com.google.ads.AdListener;
+import com.google.ads.AdRequest;
+import com.google.ads.AdRequest.ErrorCode;
+import com.google.ads.AdRequest.Gender;
+import com.google.ads.AdSize;
+import com.google.ads.AdView;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+import java.text.SimpleDateFormat;
+import java.util.GregorianCalendar;
+
+public class AdMobAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdListener
+{
+  public AdMobAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  protected String birthdayForAdViewTargeting()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getBirthDate() != null) {
+      return new SimpleDateFormat("yyyyMMdd").format(AdViewTargeting.getBirthDate().getTime());
+    }
+    return null;
+  }
+  
+  protected AdRequest.Gender genderForAdViewTargeting()
+  {
+    switch (AdViewTargeting.getGender())
+    {
+    default: 
+      return null;
+    case MALE: 
+      return AdRequest.Gender.MALE;
+    }
+    return AdRequest.Gender.FEMALE;
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into AdMob");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localObject = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localObject == null);
+    Object localObject = new AdView((Activity)localObject, AdSize.BANNER, this.ration.key);
+    ((AdView)localObject).setAdListener(this);
+    ((AdView)localObject).loadAd(requestForAdWhirlLayout(localAdViewLayout));
+  }
+  
+  public void onDismissScreen(Ad paramAd) {}
+  
+  public void onFailedToReceiveAd(Ad paramAd, AdRequest.ErrorCode paramErrorCode)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdMob fail");
+    }
+    paramAd.setAdListener(null);
+    paramAd = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAd == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAd.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramAd.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onLeaveApplication(Ad paramAd) {}
+  
+  public void onPresentScreen(Ad paramAd) {}
+  
+  public void onReceiveAd(Ad paramAd)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdMob success");
+    }
+    paramAd.setAdListener(null);
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    while (!(paramAd instanceof AdView)) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAd = (AdView)paramAd;
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, paramAd));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+  
+  protected AdRequest requestForAdWhirlLayout(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout)
+  {
+    return new AdRequest();
+  }
+}

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.util.Log;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.AdArea;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import com.energysource.szj.embeded.AdListener;
+import com.energysource.szj.embeded.AdManager;
+import com.energysource.szj.embeded.AdView;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class AdTouchAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdListener
+{
+  private int area = 81;
+  
+  public AdTouchAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void failedReceiveAd(AdView paramAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdTouch fail");
+    }
+    AdManager.setAdListener(null);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into AdTouch");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Activity localActivity;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localActivity = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localActivity == null);
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      AdManager.openDebug();
+    }
+    AdManager.openPermissionJudge();
+    AdManager.initAd(localActivity, this.ration.key);
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getAdArea() == AdViewTargeting.AdArea.BOTTOM) {}
+    for (this.area = 81;; this.area = 49)
+    {
+      AdManager.addAd(101, 1000, this.area, 0, 0);
+      AdManager.setAdListener(this);
+      AdManager.openAllAdView();
+      localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+      localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+      return;
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void receiveAd(AdView paramAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdTouch success");
+    }
+    AdManager.setAdListener(null);
+    paramAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdView.reportImpression();
+  }
+}

+  {

+    {
+      adapter.click();
+      return;
+    }
+    throw new Exception("On Click failed");
+  }

+
+import android.graphics.Color;
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;

+  implements KyAdView.onAdListener
+{
+  public AdViewHouseAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into AdViewHouse");
+    }
+    Object localObject = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localObject == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    Extra localExtra = ((AdViewLayout)localObject).extra;
+    int i = Color.rgb(localExtra.bgRed, localExtra.bgGreen, localExtra.bgBlue);
+    int j = Color.rgb(localExtra.fgRed, localExtra.fgGreen, localExtra.fgBlue);
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {}
+    for (localObject = new KyAdView(((AdViewLayout)localObject).getContext(), this.ration.key, this.ration.key2, this.ration.logo, localExtra.cycleTime, true, i, j);; localObject = new KyAdView(((AdViewLayout)localObject).getContext(), this.ration.key, this.ration.key2, this.ration.logo, localExtra.cycleTime, false, i, j))
+    {
+      ((KyAdView)localObject).setAdListener(this);
+      ((KyAdView)localObject).setHorizontalScrollBarEnabled(false);
+      ((KyAdView)localObject).setVerticalScrollBarEnabled(false);
+      return;
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void onConnectFailed(KyAdView paramKyAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdViewHouse failure");
+    }
+    paramKyAdView.setAdListener(null);
+    paramKyAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramKyAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramKyAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramKyAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onReceivedAd(KyAdView paramKyAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "AdViewHouse success");
+    }
+    paramKyAdView.setAdListener(null);
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, paramKyAdView));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+}

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import cn.aduu.adsdk.AdManager;
+import cn.aduu.adsdk.AdView;
+import cn.aduu.adsdk.AdViewListener;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class AduuAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdViewListener
+{
+  private AdView adView = null;
+  
+  public AduuAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Aduu");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Activity localActivity;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localActivity = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localActivity == null);
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      AdManager.init(localActivity, this.ration.key, this.ration.key2, -9, 0, 2, 61, true);
+    }
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      this.adView = new AdView((Activity)localAdViewLayout.getContext(), null);
+      this.adView.setAdViewListener(this);
+      localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, this.adView));
+      return;
+      AdManager.init(localActivity, this.ration.key, this.ration.key2, -9, 0, 2, 61, false);
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void onAdSwitch() {}
+  
+  public void onReceiveFail(int paramInt)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "aduu--onFailedToReceiveAd");
+    }
+    this.adView.setAdViewListener(null);
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onReceiveSuccess()

+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import android.view.ViewGroup;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Extra;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import com.adwo.adsdk.AdListener;
+import com.adwo.adsdk.AdwoAdView;
+import com.adwo.adsdk.ErrorCode;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class AdwoAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdListener
+{
+  public AdwoAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Adwo");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    while ((Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get() == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    Object localObject = localAdViewLayout.extra;
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      localObject = new AdwoAdView((Activity)localAdViewLayout.getContext(), this.ration.key, true, ((Extra)localObject).cycleTime);
+    }
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      ((AdwoAdView)localObject).setListener(this);
+      localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, (ViewGroup)localObject));
+      return;
+      if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.NORMAL) {
+        localObject = new AdwoAdView((Activity)localAdViewLayout.getContext(), this.ration.key, false, ((Extra)localObject).cycleTime);
+      } else {
+        localObject = new AdwoAdView((Activity)localAdViewLayout.getContext(), this.ration.key, false, ((Extra)localObject).cycleTime);
+      }
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void onFailedToReceiveAd(AdwoAdView paramAdwoAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onFailedToReceiveAd");
+    }
+    paramAdwoAdView.setListener(null);
+    paramAdwoAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdwoAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdwoAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramAdwoAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onFailedToReceiveAd(AdwoAdView paramAdwoAdView, ErrorCode paramErrorCode)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onFailedToReceiveAd, arg1=" + paramErrorCode);
+    }
+    paramAdwoAdView.setListener(null);
+    paramAdwoAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdwoAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdwoAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramAdwoAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onFailedToReceiveRefreshedAd(AdwoAdView paramAdwoAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onFailedToReceiveRefreshedAd");
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void onReceiveAd(AdwoAdView paramAdwoAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "onReceiveAd");
+    }
+    paramAdwoAdView.setListener(null);
+    paramAdwoAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdwoAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdwoAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    paramAdwoAdView.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }

+  }

+  {

+  }

+    }
+    this.airAD.setAirADListener(null);
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }

+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, this.airAD));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }

+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.content.Context;
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import cn.domob.android.ads.DomobAdListener;
+import cn.domob.android.ads.DomobAdView;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class DomobAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements DomobAdListener
+{
+  public DomobAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Domob");
+    }
+    Object localObject = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localObject == null) {}
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localObject = (Activity)((AdViewLayout)localObject).activityReference.get();
+    } while (localObject == null);
+    localObject = new DomobAdView((Context)localObject, this.ration.key, "320x50");
+    ((DomobAdView)localObject).setOnAdListener(this);
+    ((DomobAdView)localObject).requestRefreshAd();
+  }
+  
+  public void onFailedToReceiveFreshAd(DomobAdView paramDomobAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Domob failure");
+    }
+    paramDomobAdView.setOnAdListener(null);
+    paramDomobAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramDomobAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramDomobAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramDomobAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onLandingPageClose() {}
+  
+  public void onLandingPageOpening() {}
+  
+  public void onReceivedFreshAd(DomobAdView paramDomobAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Domob success");
+    }
+    paramDomobAdView.setOnAdListener(null);
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, paramDomobAdView));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+}

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+class FetchSuizongADRunnable
+  implements Runnable
+{
+  private Ration ration;
+  private SuizongInterfaceAdapter suizongADAdapter;
+  
+  public FetchSuizongADRunnable(SuizongInterfaceAdapter paramSuizongInterfaceAdapter, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    this.suizongADAdapter = paramSuizongInterfaceAdapter;
+    this.ration = paramRation;
+  }
+  
+  public void run()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "FetchSuizongADRunnable");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.suizongADAdapter.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    this.suizongADAdapter.requestSuizongAD(localAdViewLayout, this.ration.key);
+    if (this.suizongADAdapter.suizongAD.status.equals("1"))
+    {
+      localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new DisplaySuizongADRunnable(this.suizongADAdapter));
+      return;
+    }
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "FetchSuizongAD failure");
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.content.Context;
+import android.graphics.Color;
+import android.os.Handler;
+import android.util.Log;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Extra;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import com.fractalist.android.ads.ADView;
+import com.fractalist.android.ads.AdStatusListener;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class FractalAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdStatusListener
+{
+  ADView view;
+  
+  public FractalAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void fullScreenAdClose(boolean paramBoolean) {}
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Fractal");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Object localObject;
+    int i;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localObject = localAdViewLayout.extra;
+      i = Color.rgb(((Extra)localObject).bgRed, ((Extra)localObject).bgGreen, ((Extra)localObject).bgBlue);
+      localObject = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localObject == null);
+    ADView.setPublishId(this.ration.key);
+    this.view = new ADView((Context)localObject);
+    this.view.setFreshInterval(30);
+    this.view.setFadeImage(false);
+    this.view.setBackgroundColor(i);
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, this.view));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+  
+  public void onClick() {}
+  
+  public void onFail()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Fractal failure");
+    }
+    this.view.setAdStatusListener(null);
+    this.view = null;
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onReceiveAd()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Fractal success");
+    }
+    this.view.setAdStatusListener(null);
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+  
+  public void onRefreshAd()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Fractal, onRefreshAd");
+    }
+  }

+      return;

+          ((BannerView)localObject).refresh();

+      {
+        localAdViewLayout.rotatePriAd();
+      }
+    }
+  }

+  {

+    }

+    if (paramBannerView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramBannerView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramBannerView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }

+public class InmobiAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+{
+  private IMAdRequest mAdRequest;
+  private IMAdListener mIMAdListener = new IMAdListener()
+  {

+    {

+        Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "InMobi success");

+        return;
+      }
+      InmobiAdapter.this.mIMAdView.setLayoutParams(new RelativeLayout.LayoutParams(-1, -2));
+      localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+      localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, paramAnonymousIMAdView));
+      localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+    }
+    
+    public void onAdRequestFailed(IMAdView paramAnonymousIMAdView, IMAdRequest.ErrorCode paramAnonymousErrorCode)
+    {
+      if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+        Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "ImMobi failure");
+      }
+      paramAnonymousIMAdView.setIMAdListener(null);
+      paramAnonymousIMAdView = (AdViewLayout)InmobiAdapter.this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+      if (paramAnonymousIMAdView == null) {
+        return;
+      }
+      paramAnonymousIMAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+      paramAnonymousIMAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+    }
+    
+    public void onDismissAdScreen(IMAdView paramAnonymousIMAdView)
+    {
+      Log.i("InMobiAndroidSDK_3.0.1", "InMobiAdActivity-> onDismissAdScreen, adView: " + paramAnonymousIMAdView);
+    }
+    
+    public void onShowAdScreen(IMAdView paramAnonymousIMAdView)
+    {
+      Log.i("InMobiAndroidSDK_3.0.1", "InMobiAdActivity-> onShowAdScreen, adView: " + paramAnonymousIMAdView);
+    }
+  };
+  private IMAdView mIMAdView = null;
+  
+  public InmobiAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Inmobi");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Activity localActivity;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localActivity = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localActivity == null);
+    this.mIMAdView = new IMAdView(localActivity, 15, this.ration.key);
+    this.mAdRequest = new IMAdRequest();
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      this.mAdRequest.setTestMode(true);
+    }
+    for (;;)
+    {
+      this.mIMAdView.setIMAdRequest(this.mAdRequest);
+      this.mIMAdView.setIMAdListener(this.mIMAdListener);
+      localAdViewLayout.addView(this.mIMAdView);
+      this.mIMAdView.setLayoutParams(new RelativeLayout.LayoutParams(0, 0));
+      return;
+      if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.NORMAL) {
+        this.mAdRequest.setTestMode(false);
+      } else {
+        this.mAdRequest.setTestMode(false);
+      }
+    }
+  }

+  public void requestSuizongAD(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, String paramString)
+  {
+    try
+    {
+      if (TextUtils.isEmpty(ip)) {
+        ip = getLocalIPAddress();
+      }
+      this.suizongScreenManager = new SuizongScreenManager(paramAdViewLayout.adViewManager.width);
+      HashMap localHashMap = new HashMap();
+      localHashMap.put("appkey", paramString);
+      localHashMap.put("uuid", paramAdViewLayout.adViewManager.mDeviceid);
+      localHashMap.put("client", "2");
+      localHashMap.put("ip", ip);
+      localHashMap.put("density", String.valueOf(this.density));
+      localHashMap.put("pw", Integer.toString(paramAdViewLayout.adViewManager.width));
+      localHashMap.put("ph", Integer.toString(paramAdViewLayout.adViewManager.height));
+      localHashMap.put("aw", this.suizongScreenManager.getAw());
+      localHashMap.put("ah", this.suizongScreenManager.getAh());
+      localHashMap.put("sdk", "adview_1.7.1");
+      localHashMap.put("pcheck", makePcheck(localHashMap));
+      localHashMap.put("icheck", MD5.MD5Encode(makePcheck(localHashMap) + this.serial_key));
+      url = "http://api.suizong.com/mobile/ADServerGetAPI";
+      httpRequest(localHashMap, "request");
+      if (!this.suizongAD.status.equals("1")) {
+        return;
+      }
+      paramAdViewLayout = new HashMap();
+      paramAdViewLayout.put("adid", this.suizongAD.adid);
+      paramAdViewLayout.put("updatetime", this.suizongAD.updateTime);
+      paramAdViewLayout.put("sid", this.suizongAD.sid);
+      paramString = makePcheck4GetBody(paramAdViewLayout);
+      paramAdViewLayout.put("pcheck", paramString);
+      paramAdViewLayout.put("icheck", MD5.MD5Encode(paramString + this.serial_key));
+      url = "http://api.suizong.com/mobile/ADServerGetBodyAPI";
+      httpRequest(paramAdViewLayout, "getbody");
+      url = "http://api.suizong.com/mobile/ADServerShowAPI";
+      new Thread()
+      {
+        public void run()
+        {
+          HashMap localHashMap = new HashMap();
+          localHashMap.put("adid", SuizongInterfaceAdapter.this.suizongAD.adid);
+          localHashMap.put("updatetime", SuizongInterfaceAdapter.this.suizongAD.updateTime);
+          localHashMap.put("sid", SuizongInterfaceAdapter.this.suizongAD.sid);
+          String str = SuizongInterfaceAdapter.this.makePcheck4GetBody(localHashMap);
+          localHashMap.put("pcheck", str);
+          localHashMap.put("icheck", MD5.MD5Encode(str + SuizongInterfaceAdapter.this.serial_key));
+          SuizongInterfaceAdapter.this.httpRequest(localHashMap, "imps");
+        }
+      }.start();
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (Exception paramAdViewLayout)
+    {
+      paramAdViewLayout.printStackTrace();
+    }
+  }

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+class SuizongScreenManager
+{
+  private String ah = "48";
+  private String aw = "320";
+  private int screenWidth = -1;
+  
+  public SuizongScreenManager(int paramInt)
+  {
+    this.screenWidth = paramInt;
+    calc();
+  }
+  
+  private void calc()
+  {
+    if (this.screenWidth <= 480)
+    {
+      this.aw = "320";
+      this.ah = "48";
+    }
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      if (this.screenWidth < 728)
+      {
+        this.aw = "468";
+        this.ah = "60";
+        return;
+      }
+    } while (this.screenWidth < 728);
+    this.aw = "728";
+    this.ah = "90";
+  }
+  
+  public String getAh()
+  {
+    return this.ah;
+  }
+  
+  public String getAw()
+  {
+    return this.aw;
+  }
+  
+  public void setAh(String paramString)
+  {
+    this.ah = paramString;
+  }
+  
+  public void setAw(String paramString)
+  {
+    this.aw = paramString;
+  }
+}

+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Object localObject;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localObject = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localObject == null);
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      AdManager.setTest(true);
+    }
+    for (;;)

+      AdManager.setPublisherKey(this.ration.key);

+      localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+      localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, (ViewGroup)localObject));
+      localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+      return;
+      AdManager.setTest(false);
+    }
+  }

+public class UmengAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter

+{

+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {

+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Object localObject;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localObject = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localObject == null);
+    if (localAdViewLayout.umengView == null)
+    {
+      localObject = new AdView((Context)localObject);

+      localAdViewLayout.umengView = ((RelativeLayout)localObject);
+    }
+    localAdViewLayout.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, localAdViewLayout.umengView));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }

+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Umeng failure");
+    }

+    paramAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+

+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();

+package com.adview.adapters;
+
+import android.app.Activity;
+import android.content.Context;
+import android.util.Log;
+import android.widget.RelativeLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewLayout;
+import com.adview.AdViewManager;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting;
+import com.adview.AdViewTargeting.RunMode;
+import com.adview.obj.Ration;
+import com.vpon.adon.android.AdListener;
+import com.vpon.adon.android.AdOnPlatform;
+import com.vpon.adon.android.AdView;
+import java.lang.ref.WeakReference;
+
+public class VponAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+  implements AdListener
+{
+  public VponAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Vpon");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {}
+    Object localObject;
+    do
+    {
+      return;
+      localObject = (Activity)localAdViewLayout.activityReference.get();
+    } while (localObject == null);
+    try
+    {
+      localObject = new AdView((Context)localObject);
+      ((AdView)localObject).setLicenseKey(this.ration.key, AdOnPlatform.CN, false, false);
+      ((AdView)localObject).setAdListener(this);
+      localAdViewLayout.AddSubView((RelativeLayout)localObject);
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (IllegalArgumentException localIllegalArgumentException)
+    {
+      localAdViewLayout.rollover();
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void onFailedToRecevieAd(AdView paramAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Vpon fail");
+    }
+    paramAdView.setAdListener(null);
+    paramAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover_pri();
+    paramAdView.rotateThreadedPri();
+  }
+  
+  public void onRecevieAd(AdView paramAdView)
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Vpon success");
+    }
+    paramAdView.setAdListener(null);
+    paramAdView = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (paramAdView == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    paramAdView.reportImpression();
+    paramAdView.adViewManager.resetRollover();
+    paramAdView.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+}

+
+public class WiyunAdapter
+  extends AdViewAdapter
+{
+  public WiyunAdapter(AdViewLayout paramAdViewLayout, Ration paramRation)
+  {
+    super(paramAdViewLayout, paramRation);
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {
+    if (AdViewTargeting.getRunMode() == AdViewTargeting.RunMode.TEST) {
+      Log.d("AdView SDK v1.7.4", "Into Wiyun");
+    }
+    AdViewLayout localAdViewLayout = (AdViewLayout)this.adViewLayoutReference.get();
+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }
+    Object localObject = localAdViewLayout.extra;
+    int i = Color.rgb(((Extra)localObject).bgRed, ((Extra)localObject).bgGreen, ((Extra)localObject).bgBlue);
+    int j = Color.rgb(((Extra)localObject).fgRed, ((Extra)localObject).fgGreen, ((Extra)localObject).fgBlue);

+    if (localAdViewLayout == null) {
+      return;
+    }

+    localAdViewLayout.handler.post(new AdViewLayout.ViewAdRunnable(localAdViewLayout, paramZestADZAdView));
+    localAdViewLayout.rotateThreadedDelayed();
+  }
+  
+  public void handle()
+  {

+          return;
+        }
+        return;

+      catch (IllegalArgumentException localIllegalArgumentException)
+      {
+        localAdViewLayout.rollover();
+      }
+    }

+  {
+    int i = paramRation.priority;
+    if (this.priority < i) {
+      return -1;
+    }
+    if (this.priority > i) {
+      return 1;
+    }
+    return 0;
+  }

+    paramCanvas.restore();
+  }
